  "prompt": "How do I recover my Gmail password with a recovery mobile number and a Gmail address?",
  "response": "To recover your Gmail password using a recovery mobile number and Gmail address, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Visit the Google Account Recovery Page:**\n   - Go to the Google Account Recovery page by visiting [accounts.google.com/signin/recovery](https://accounts.google.com/signin/recovery).\n\n2. **Enter Your Email Address:**\n   - Enter the Gmail address for which you need to recover the password and click on \u201cNext.\u201d\n\n3. **Select Recovery Method:**\n   - You will be prompted to try signing in. Click on \"Forgot password?\"\n\n4. **Verify Using Recovery Methods:**\n   - **Using Recovery Phone Number:**\n     - Google will suggest sending a verification code to your recovery phone number. Make sure the number displayed is yours and accessible, then select it.\n     - You will receive a text message (SMS) with a verification code. Enter this code in the space provided on the account recovery page.\n     \n   - **Using Recovery Email Address:**\n     - If you choose to use your recovery email address, Google will send a verification code to that address.\n     - Check your Gmail account (recovery email) for the verification code, then enter it on the account recovery page.\n\n5. **Reset Your Password:**\n   - After successfully verifying your identity with either method, you will be prompted to set a new password.\n   - Choose a strong password that you haven't used before and confirm it by entering it again.\n\n6. **Complete the Recovery Process:**\n   - Once you\u2019ve reset your password, you will be redirected to your account\u2019s login page to sign in with your new password.\n\n**Tips for a Strong Password:**\n- Use a mix of upper and lower case letters, numbers, and symbols.\n- Avoid using easily guessed information such as birthdays or common words.\n- Aim for at least 12 characters to enhance security.\n\n**Additional Security Measures:**\n- After regaining access, ensure your recovery information (phone number, alternate email) is up to date.\n- Consider enabling 2-Step Verification for added account security.\n\nIf you encounter any issues during this process, follow the on-screen instructions or visit the Google Help Center for additional support.",
